'''疊氮化銣'''是一種[[無機化合物|無機化合物]]，是一種[[疊氮化合物|疊氮化合物]]，其分子式為{{化學式|銣|氮|3|link=}}。

== 制備 ==
它可以透過[[碳酸銣|碳酸銣]]和[[疊氮化鈉|疊氮化鈉]]的複分解反應製備<ref name="Balzer">Dissertation: "Strukturchemische Untersuchungen von Halogenidaziden des Bariums, Thalliums und Zinks", Universität Dortmund, 2001. [http://www.google.at/url?sa=t&source=web&cd=12&ved=0CEwQFjAL&url=http%3A%2F%2Fdeposit.ddb.de%2Fcgi-bin%2Fdokserv%3Fidn%3D962892645%26dok_var%3Dd1%26dok_ext%3Dpdf%26filename%3D962892645.pdf&rct=j&q=Rubidiumazid&ei=Oq4oTIKdIJqhONChjcMC&usg=AFQjCNGYobyF05Nvmz1PtBRMdrIYpulGGg PDF]</ref>：
:{{反應式|Rb|{{官能基|C|O|3|link=碳酸根}}|+|Na|{{官能基|N|3|link=叠氮化合物}}|→|Rb|{{官能基|N|3|link=叠氮化合物}}|+|Na|{{官能基|C|O|3|link=碳酸根}}}}

'''疊氮化銣'''會在氮的影響下的放電，形成[[氮化銣|氮化銣]]。<ref name="Wattenberg">H. Wattenberg: "Über zwei Bildungsweisen von Natriumnitrid und Kaliumnitrid" in ''Ber. d. dt. chem. Ges.'' '''1930''', ''63''(7), S. 1667-1672. {{doi|
10.1002/cber.19300630708}}</ref>

==性質==
===物理性質===
'''疊氮化銣'''的晶體結構為[[四方晶系|四方晶系]]，空間群I4/mcm，晶格參數為 a =630.8 pm，C=753.7 pm，每單位晶胞有4個單位<ref name="Lax"/><ref name="Müller">Ulrich Müller: "Verfeinerung der Kristallstrukturen von KN<sub>3</sub>, RbN<sub>3</sub>, CsN<sub>3</sub> und TlN<sub>3</sub>" in ''Zeitschr. f. anorg. u. allg. Chem.'' '''1972''', ''392''(2), S. 159-166. {{doi|10.1002/zaac.19723920207}}</ref>，這和[[疊氮化鋰|疊氮化鋰]]、[[疊氮化鈉|疊氮化鈉]]、[[疊氮化鉀|疊氮化鉀]]類似<ref name='疊氮化銣、疊氮化鉀、疊氮化鋰具有相似結構'/>。[[File:Lithium-azide-unit-cell-3D-balls.png|left]]的晶格<ref>{{ cite journal | journal = Acta Cryst. | volume = B'''24''' | issue = 2 | pages = 262–269 | doi = 10.1107/S0567740868002062 | title = The crystal structures of lithium, sodium and strontium azides | first1 = G. E. | last1= Pringle |  first2 = D. E. | last2 = Noakes |date=February 1968}}</ref>'''疊氮化銣'''也是和[[疊氮化鉀|疊氮化鉀]]、[[疊氮化鋰|疊氮化鋰]]一樣是四方結構<ref name='疊氮化銣、疊氮化鉀、疊氮化鋰具有相似結構'>{{cite journal | last=Khilji | first=M. Y. | last2=Sherman | first2=W. F. | last3=Wilkinson | first3=G. R. | title=Variable temperature and pressure Raman spectra of potassium azide KN3 | url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-raman-spectroscopy_1982-06_12_3/page/300 | journal=Journal of Raman Spectroscopy | publisher=Wiley-Blackwell | volume=12 | issue=3 | year=1982 | issn=0377-0486 | doi=10.1002/jrs.1250120319 | pages=300–303}}</ref>]]{{padright:|70|
}}

== 化學性質 ==
